description:
Includes 10 arranged songs from "Touhou Seirensen ~ Undefined Fantastic Object." as additional download contents for "Groove Coaster Wai Wai Party !!!!".

This pack includes the following content.
■Songs Pack (10 songs)
 - Mouth to mouth / Yuuhei Satellite
 - Parasol Memories / Chocofan
 - Hashiru / Butaotome
 - Endless Seeker / A-One
 - Gekitsui Murasa / beatMARIO
 - Aitsu Wa Ikasama Wo Shiteiru / TaNaBaTa
 - Sad Rain / REDALiCE
 - FOUR SEASONS OF LONELINESS verβ feat. Sariyajin / TatshMusicCircle
 - Mikakunin Gensou Coaster / t+pazolite(C.H.S/ALiCE'S EMOTiON) × beatMARIO(COOL&CREATE)
 - Touhou Seirensen / MASAKI (ZUNTATA) *Locked

■Navigators
 - KOGASA
 - BYAKUREN

■Avatars
 - KOGASA(2D)
 - MURASA(2D)
 - SYOU(2D)
 - BYAKUREN(2D)
 - NUE(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Touhou Project Arrangements Pack 8
